<div>
  <div class="header">
    <p class="date">{{momentDateFormat currentDate "DD MMM YYYY"}}</p>
  </div>

  <p class="address">
    {{recipient.firstName}}
    {{recipient.initials}}
    {{recipient.lastName}}
    <br />
    {{recipient.address1}}
    {{#if recipient.address2}}
      <br />
      {{recipient.address2}}
    {{/if}}
    <br />
    {{recipient.city}},
    {{recipient.province}}
    <br />
    {{recipient.country}},
    {{recipient.postalCode}}
  </p>

  <p class="saluation">
    Dear
    {{recipient.firstName}}:
  </p>

  <p>
    I am pleased to inform you that your Yukon Grant application to attend full-time post-secondary has been approved as
    follows:
  </p>

  <p>
    <span class="flex justify-between">
      <strong>Program: {{program.name}}</strong>
      <span>
        <strong>Start Date:</strong>
        <span class="ml-4">{{momentDateFormat program.startDate "MMM Do, YYYY"}}</span>
      </span>
    </span>
    <span class="flex justify-between">
      <strong>Institution: {{program.institutionName}}</strong>
      <span>
        <strong>End Date:</strong>
        <span class="ml-4">{{momentDateFormat program.endDate "MMM Do, YYYY"}}</span>
      </span>
    </span>

    {{#each assessments}}
      <span class="flex mt-1"></span>
      {{#if (hasManyElements @root.assessments)}}
        {{#if @first}}
          <span class="flex">Current Assessment</span>
        {{else}}
          <span class="flex">Previous Assessment: {{momentDateFormat this.assessedDate "MMM Do, YYYY"}}</span>
        {{/if}}
      {{/if}}
      <span>
        <strong style="inline-block w-[150px]">Rate per Week:</strong>
        <span>{{centsToDollarString this.ratePerWeekInCents}}</span>
      </span>
      <br />
      <span>
        <strong style="inline-block w-[150px]">Approv. Weeks:</strong>
        <span>{{this.approvalWeeks}}</span>
      </span>
      <br />
      <span>
        <strong style="inline-block w-[150px]">Travel/Airfare:</strong>
        <span>{{centsToDollarString this.travelAndAirFairCostInCents}}</span>
      </span>
    {{/each}}
  </p>

  {{#if disbursements}}
    <table class="">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Disbursements<span class="ml-4"></span></th>
          <th>Issue Date - Based on confirmed enrollment before each semester</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each disbursements}}
          <tr>
            <td>{{centsToDollarString this.amountInCents}}</td>
            <td>{{momentDateFormatDefault this.releaseDate "MMM YYYY" "Upon confirmation"}}</td>
          </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  {{/if}}

  <p>
    If any of the above information is incorrect or you withdraw from full-time studies or drop to part-time status, you
    may have to repay some or all of your Yukon Grant.
  </p>

  <p>
    Your first disbursement has been processed.
    <strong>If more than one payment is listed above, you will be required to submit a Program Information Form (PIF)
      confirming full-time status prior to the release of any subsequent disbursements.
    </strong>
    Our office will accept PIFs completed by the institution and submitted directly to
    <a href="mailto:sfa@yukon.ca">sfa@yukon.ca</a>
    as early as one month before the issue date(s) outlined above, and no later than the end date of your approved
    funding period. Pending payments will be cancelled if not processed before the end date. You can download the PIF at
    <a
      href="http://yukon.ca/en/program-information-student-financial-assistance"
    >http://yukon.ca/en/program-information-student-financial-assistance</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you have any questions regarding your assessment, please contact our office by email at
    <a href="mailto:sfa@yukon.ca">sfa@yukon.ca</a>, by telephone at
    <a href="tel:867-667-5929">867-667-5929</a>, or toll free within Yukon at
    <a href="tel:1-800-661-0408">1-800-661-0408</a>
    ext. 5929.
  </p>

  <p>
    Congratulations on your decision to further your education. On behalf of the Department of Education, I wish you the
    very best in your studies.
  </p>

  <p>
    Sincerely,
  </p>
  <p class="mt-10">
    {{studentFinancialAssistanceOfficer.firstName}}
    {{studentFinancialAssistanceOfficer.lastName}}
    <br />
    {{#if studentFinancialAssistanceOfficer.position}}
      {{studentFinancialAssistanceOfficer.position}}
    {{else}}
      Student Financial Services Officer
    {{/if}}
    <br />
    Department of Education, Government of Yukon
  </p>
</div>